  "23-17": (
    caption: [Energy sources for muscle contraction. Different fuels are used for ATP synthesis during bursts of heavy activity and during light activity or rest. Phosphocreatine can rapidly supply ATP. c23HormonalRegulationAndIntegrationOfMammalianMetabolism.indd Page 946 25/10/12 11:16 AM user-F408 c23HormonalRegulationAndIntegrationOfMammalianMetabolism.indd Page 946 25/10/12 11:16 AM user-F408 /Users/user-F408/Desktop /Users/user-F408/Desktop 946],
