    caption: [The fuels that supply ATP in the brain. The energy source used by the brain varies with nutritional state. The ketone body used dur- ing starvation is (cid:2)-hydroxybutyrate. Electrogenic transport by the Na(cid:2)K(cid:2) ATPase maintains the transmembrane potential essential to information transfer among neurons. (a) (b) 12.00 2.00],
