    caption: [Metabolic integration by PPARs. The three PPAR isoforms regulate lipid and glucose homeostasis through their coordinated effects on gene expression in liver, muscle, and adipose tissue. PPAR(cid:3) and PPAR(cid:6) (and its closely related isoform PPAR(cid:2)) regulate lipid utilization; PPAR(cid:4) regulates lipid storage and the insulin sensitivity of various tissues.],
